snippet.title: Travis Pastrana's House! | Freeride Gameplay | MTX Mototrax
snippet.description:
You wanted it, so I brought it! MTX Mototrax returns on the channel, and today we're doing a freeride. I decided to do a freeride at Travis Pastrana's House, because this was one of the coolest freeride spots in any motocross game. Everybody dreams of riding at Pastrana's, but in MTX Mototrax, you can do it! You guys wanted more mtx mototrax, so I brought it back for you all! Thanks for all the support on the channel!
__
